<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>باب {عُتُلٍّ بَعْدَ ذَلِكَ زَنِيمٍ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[القلم: ١٣]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
